<li id="cite_note-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://languagesgulper.com/eng/Niger.html">"Niger-Congo Languages"</a>, "The Language Gulper", March 2015</span>
